<br>
To those who are certain they are right on these subjects, I can say only one thing: you are certainly wrong. This shouldn't come as earthshaking news to you but it would be wise of you to recognise and accept it.<br>
<br>
If you can't then maybe you will have to recognise the painful truth that you are a narrow minded bigot. For that is how others who do not agree with you (ie. almost everyone) will see you.<br>
<br>
I don't presume to know the absolute truth of things. I think I am closer to understanding than many who spoke here but we all feel that way, I guess. But I can respect the ideas, opinions and beliefs of those who respect other's.<br>
